In the case of 3D materials, we apply our model to monoatomic metallic materials covering common cubic crystal structures: Pd[FCC], Au[FCC] and Na[BCC]. Figure 2 shows the learning curve for these three structures with a supercell of 3 × 3 × 3 and symmetry groups T3×3×3(3)×Oh\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
