				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${{{{{{{\bf{k}}}}}}}}\left({{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}},{{{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}}}^{\prime}\right)={\nabla }_{{{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}}}{k}_{E}\left({{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}},{{{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}}}^{\prime}\right){\nabla }_{{{{{{{{{\bf{x}}}}}}}}}^{\prime}}^{\top }$$\end{document} that models any force field fF as a transformation of some unknown PES fE such that,2fF=−∇fE~GP−∇μE(x),∇xkEx,x′∇x′⊤.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
